terms.name: Tuning Frequency (MHz)
terms.explanation: Frequency used to tune the harvester input, in megahertz.

terms.name: Target Voltage (mV)
terms.explanation: Desired output or operating voltage target, in millivolts.

terms.name: Harvester Source
terms.explanation: Type used at the input of the harvester.

terms.name: Measured Frequency (MHz)
terms.explanation: Operating or measured frequency of the input signal, in megahertz.

terms.name: Input Power (dBm)
terms.explanation: Input power level at the harvester input, expressed in dBm.

terms.name: Buffer Voltage (mV)
terms.explanation: Voltage measured at the buffer node, in millivolts.

terms.name: Resistance
terms.explanation: Load or equivalent resistance value in ohms.

terms.name: DC Output Power (pW)
terms.explanation: DC Power value expressed in picowatts.

terms.name: Efficiency
terms.explanation: Energy conversion efficiency of the harvester setup.
